hopobject.body: The United States tylenol dosing drugs.com In his Mansion House speech to the City last month, the Chancellor gave the green light to the first stage of the privatisation of the Treasury's 39% stake in Lloyds, signalling that it would be initiated by a large placing of shares with mainstream investment institutions rather than retail investors, probably before the end of the year - so long as Lloyds' share price continues to rise.
